show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/8XnwMd
show.description:
A wealthy woman discovers her beloved daughter is trapped in the grip of a charming but violent husband. Justice doesn’t come from the courts—but from a mother’s silent fury.
“Mother of Revenge” is a chilling tale where love turns into vengeance, and silence carries the deadliest scream.
